Product description

Smart Watch for Men Women Fitness Tracker Make/Answer Call Watch IP68 Waterproof Smart Watch With Heart Rate Blood Pressure Spo2 Sleep Tracker

Features:

1. Full Touch Fitness Watch: Stylish and Simple Appearance, 1.85" HD Full Touch Screen. Easy Control with the Sensitive Touch Screen. Watch screen will light up every time you raise your hand.

2. Bluetooth Call Smartwatch: You can directly use this watch to answer make calls/play music/read messages/store contacts/view call history.

3. Music Playback and Control: You can carry music directly through the watch.

4. Pedometer Step Tracker Watch: Track your steps, calories burned, distance, pace, heart rate change, duration of movement.

5. 112+ Modes Activity Tracker: Support 112+ Multi-Sport Modes (walking, running, cycling, Basketball,et.)

6. Heart Rate/Blood Oxygen Monitor Watch: 24 hours continuous monitoring.

7. Sleep Monitor Watch: Automatically monitor and analyze sleep quality during night.

8. Alarm: Can set up to multiple Alarm Clocks.

9. Smart Watch with Notifications: Receive Call / SMS Notification from Facebook, Twitter, Whatsapp,LinkedIn, Instagram etc.(Can not reply it)

10.IP68 Water Resistant : IP68 waterproof, which has a good waterproof effect for daily life, such as: washing hands, anti-sweat, anti-rain, etc.

11. Breathe Training: Relax yourself and have a break when you feel nervous or pressure.

Bluetooth smartwatch with text and call

  1. With this bluetooth call smartwatch, you don't miss any important calls,by using clear waterproof speakers. You can make, answer and refuse a call on your wrist, also receive message/app notification(including SMS,Whatsapp, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Facebook messaging, LinkedIn, and more). Never miss a call and a message. In addition, you can also listen to music directly through the smart watch, get lost in the music, enjoy a colorful and intelligent life.
  2. With all notifications displayed on your wrist and alerted by vibration, you can keep your phone in your pocket without missing any important calls or messages when you're out walking, exercising, or seeing friends.
  3. Add Your Contacts: Smartwatch can add up to 20 frequent contacts, view recent call history, make calls from the watch dialer

Fitness watches for men women with 112+ Sport Modes

  1. This fitness tracker watch automatically and accurately track count your full-day steps, calories burned, distances, miles walked and duration to get a clear situation of your daily exercise.
  2. The square watches for men has 112+ sports modes to meet your various sports styles. You can choose the corresponding mode according to your sports (Walk,Run,on foot,Cycling,Skipping,Rope ,Work out etc.)
  3. After exercise, check the data on the exercise watch or related app (exercising time, average heart rate, distance, steps, calories).You can make better adjustments by analyzing these data.And exercise your sports data through the exercise tracker watch to arrange fitness plan.


Smartwatch with Heart Rate Monitor

  • This watch equipped with the advanced self-developed optical sensor and a powerful sensor engine, the accuracy of data monitoring has been effectively improved by 23%.
  • Our smartwatch real-time track your heart rate, blood oxygen, and sleep, pays attention to your health at all times, records physical changes, and helps you better understand your health.
  • You can also view recent data changes in the APP, as well as professional advice on your health status.Master the first-hand dynamics of heart rate, blood oxygen, to realize all-around health protection.


Sleep Tracker with Alarm Clock

  • Adopting advanced motion sensors, this watch automatically monitor sleep status (deep sleep, light sleep and wake up time, and provide a comprehensive sleep quality analysis to help you adjust your sleep habits.
  • This classic digital watch can wake you up with alarm clock, you can set up to alarms in our app.


1.85" HD Screen Customizable

  1. Choose from over 100 watch faces to match your style, or personalize your smartwatch with your own photos.
  2. 1.85" inch full touch screen. Watch face will light up automatically when you lift and twist your wrist.
  3. Easier to read with five levels of brightness options in the sun or dark.
  4. Smart watch come with 2 watch bands of different colors


IP68 Waterproof Smart Watch

This smart watch is IP68 waterproof ,you can wear it during outdoor activities, rainy day, washing hand.


Fitness watch with Countdown and stopwatch

This Smartwatch has Countdown stopwatch and timer function.Activate the stopwatch function on the screen and record the exercise time. You can also use it to calculate more things.


Remote Camera

Take a picture of your phone remotely with your smartwatch, upload the photo as your dial!

How to connect the smart watch?

A: First of all, please be sure to connect our smart watch through the "FitCloudPro" APP.

1. Tum on the "Bluetooth" function of your phone.

2. Open the "Google Play" or the APP Store".

3. Search for "FitCloudPro" APP and download it.

4. Open the APP, click "Please connect device", click "Select device",find P45pro" and bind it.

B: Perform the following steps to enable the answer/call function.

1. After selecting "P45pro"to connect, on the mobile phone system pop-up pairing request, select pairing.

2. Tum on the call Bluetooth switch on the watch (used whent he watch cannot make calls and play media sound).

3. In the phone settings, in the system bluetooth, turn on these permissions of the P45pro.

4.Once connected, you could use the watch to answer/make calls anytime.

If you don't need to use the call function, you can turn off the answer/call function so that the battery can last longer.

      The Smart Watch for Men and Women Fitness is a versatile, waterproof smartwatch designed for both active users and everyday wearers. With its sleek digital design, this watch supports making and answering calls directly from the watch, making it a convenient option for those on the go.

      Key Features:
      Waterproof: Suitable for swimming and resistant to rain, making it ideal for active users or those who want to wear it during workouts.
      Fitness Tracking: Tracks steps, running, heart rate, and other essential metrics like calories burned, making it a solid choice for fitness enthusiasts.
      Call Functionality: Supports making and receiving calls via Bluetooth connection to your smartphone, eliminating the need to pull out your phone during workouts or errands.
      Compatibility: Works seamlessly with both Android phones (Samsung, Google Pixel, etc.) and iPhones, offering wide compatibility.
      Battery Life: Offers decent battery performance, with most models lasting several days on a single charge depending on usage.
      Design: Lightweight and comfortable, making it suitable for daily wear without being too bulky.

      Pros:
      Affordable compared to high-end smartwatches.
      Great for fitness tracking with built-in GPS for running.
      Call feature is very convenient for multitasking.
      Compatible with both Android and iOS devices.

      Cons:
      May lack the advanced health sensors (e.g., ECG or blood oxygen monitoring) that higher-end models offer.
      Some models might have limited third-party app integration.

      Conclusion:

      The Smart Watch for Men and Women Fitness is a solid, budget-friendly option for those who want a reliable smartwatch with essential features like fitness tracking, waterproofing, and the ability to make calls.
